   SAMHSA logo Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration

   Acronym list...: DHHS/SAMHSA
   Web site.......: http://www.samhsa.gov

   Mission
          SAMHSA's mission is to assure that quality substance abuse and
          mental health services are available to the people who need them
          and to ensure that prevention and treatment knowledge is used
          more effectively in the general health care system.

  Parent Organizations

     * Department of Health & Human Services

  Subordinate Organizations

     * Office of the Administrator
     * Center for Mental Health Services
     * Center for Substance Abuse Prevention
     * Center for Substance Abuse Treatment
     * Office of Applied Studies
     * Office of Program Services
